text: Everyone who gets nervous before a first date.
Everyone who believes the 'who pays on the first date' debate is silly.
Everyone who has had an absolutely terrible first date.
Everyone who has had a first date turn into a long-term relationship.
Everyone who has a 'go-to' first date outfit.
Everyone who has used an excuse to end a bad first date early.
Everyone who thinks a first date kiss is a must (if it goes well).
Everyone who prefers a casual coffee/drink first date over a formal dinner.
Everyone who has ever been 'ghosted' after a first date.
Everyone who analyzes every detail of a first date afterwards with friends.
